Package com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.card

Contains the classes for creating a specialisation of a Card or list of Cards for use with a DeckOfCards or ToqNotification.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Card An abstract representation of a card used in a DeckOfCards and a ToqNotification.
ListCard A specialised type of List for maintaining a list of Cards in a DeckOfCards.
NotificationTextCard A notification implementation of a Card which is rendered as a pop-up on the Toq smartwatch, for use with a ToqNotification.
SimpleTextCard A simple text based implementation of a Card for use with a DeckOfCards.
 

Package com.qualcomm.toq.smartwatch.api.v1.deckofcards.card Description
